Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:39.87,eptitle,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(266,92)\c&H2C367D&\2c&H2F3C7B&}Snow  Storm\N at the Lodge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:06.16,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, look at the snow!  It's white all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.51,0:02:07.86,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Mikage.  It's snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.31,0:02:09.97,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.51,0:02:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They fight against a snowman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.96,0:02:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to be awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't scary at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stuffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.55,0:03:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's dump our stuff and go skiing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna hit the slope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to my lodge.  I've been expecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of the lodge my father runs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.15,0:03:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it.  I'm not done with explaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna brag, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.18,0:03:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.41,0:03:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How my sense is reflected on the construction of the lodge is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're bragging, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.  Now the climax of the festival poses a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could this path of the spirit be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not mentioned in the pamphlet at all.\NDoesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.27,0:04:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm getting the picture.  Rika, the snowman does exist after all.  Soon, we'll find one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get solid proof this time.  I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our future is promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting worse over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.99,0:04:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she's still blabbing about the door or the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:03.39,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,So, I said, I heard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:06.45,Default,Daijoji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no.  You haven't seen the design of the pillar there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:08.33,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.75,Default,Daijoji,0000,0000,0000,,No, you didn't.  Now look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:12.75,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Help, Tomomi !
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:13.75,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing we can do.
Comment: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:17.65,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, we'll find one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:20.59,Default,Daijoji,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.02,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't hear what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.23,0:05:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, a snowman.  Awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.73,0:05:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bad omen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:48.34,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:50.03,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:53.27,Default,fat boy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry.  They really don't know any manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!  Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:58.93,Default,fat boy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:05.72,Default,fat boy,0000,0000,0000,,Just in case, can I have your phone number, address, and measurements?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I'm quite OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:11.27,Default,fat boy,0000,0000,0000,,But I insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H101360&}Ms. Emma Easton, there is a phone call for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?  A rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be a mark for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could be where the snowman comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:07:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your step, Rika.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?  After all, I chose all the interior design.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See this bed cover?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, she's got something to brag about everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I envy her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's at the Rosebud inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing good over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The snowman is around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got nothing to brag about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There might be a real snowman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.  There is one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, there is one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, that's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't believe me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it'd be fun if there's one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's catch him ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we go see the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the snowman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snowman?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.51,0:08:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The snowman must have taken everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying to stop us because I found a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got F for math, didn't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you get on Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't even think about it !
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?!  Here's a powerful one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!  You missed me.  You missed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.  You dropped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Noda!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.  Nice to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.04,0:09:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, is this the way to the lodge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... no, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.55,0:09:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird.  I'd swear it was this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must've taken a wrong road.  You're heading the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading back to the snowman's cave.  Hang onto me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attend Minato International School.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's in our neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you interested in traditional Japanese culture and customs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.  Especially legends and myths are interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, do you know about the snowman legend in this region?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to find out about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a man who came to ask about the legend yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he was a school teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it'll go away that soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:12:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"yuguradoshirutoneriko"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"yuguradoshirutoneriko"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"yuguradoshirutoneriko"
Comment: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:25.24,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\c&HFFFFFF&}Matsunaga-{\i1\c&H00B3FFFF}imoto{\i0\c&HFFFFFF} = {\i1\c&H00B3FFFF}younger{\i0\c&HFFFFFF} Matsunaga = Mikage\n{\fs22\c&HFFFFFF&}Matsunaga-{\i1\c&H00B3FFFF}ane{\i0\c&HFFFFFF} = {\i1\c&H00B3FFFF}older{\i0\c&HFFFFFF} Matsunaga = Tomomi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll come in if it wants to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rika, hang in there.  I'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get it over with and have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rika.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi, you deal with that.  I'll take care of the door.  Let's go, Tomomi.
Comment: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:09.91,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"yuguradoshirutoneriko"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Comment: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:31.85,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get something to hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give it our best shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, what's the use of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.23,0:14:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.19,0:14:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a hand with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.17,0:14:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"yuguradoshirutoneriko"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mikage!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomomi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mikage, do you hear it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah.  What is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"yuguradoshirutoneriko"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta nail it down from outside.  Can you get Noda?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emma, can you find a hammer and some nails?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.38,0:16:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rika, we're getting there.  I see the old lady's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daijoji, what's wrong?  What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda, Yamagishi needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying and tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need some firewood.  Something to keep the fire going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must keep the fire going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Daijoji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looked like she was scared of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looked like a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We ran out of firewood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Firewood is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That ought to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were those bums?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no way to treat ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some stranger came in...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did they do to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just threw us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Mikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Emma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.  You two go downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off.  Can't you stay still?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:18:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some big kids they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.38,0:20:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda.\NYamagashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.51,0:20:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she jumped from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher!
Comment: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:49.12,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,to be continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came for skiing and we haven't at all !
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen in this mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.76,0:21:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something big and something wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.15,0:22:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Miracle Girls,\N{\i1\c&HFFFF00&} "Avalanche  Warning"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.54,0:22:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is an avalanche wonderful?
