Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:07.92,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.36,0:22:11.41,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
