Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.25,0:22:58.05,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,When we can't say "I'm sorry,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.47,0:23:03.17,notes,Credit,0000,0000,0046,,{\a7}Subtitled by Studio Hooseki.\Nwww.miwasoft.com/hooseki
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.16,0:23:05.63,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,we send out feelings through the little fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:11.24,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,Going over the tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.03,0:23:14.61,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,we want to be honest to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.03,0:23:20.40,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause the sky deserves a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:22.91,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:26.48,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.44,0:23:29.61,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,Two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:33.78,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,are better than one of us.
